 guide and recipes. 0aAmishvFiction. 0aMan-woman relationshipsvFiction. 0aLarge type books. 7aLove stories.2gsafd 7aChristian fiction.2gsafd1 aGray, Shelley Shepard.tAmish brides of Pinecraft ;vbk. 3.